Third-Party Notices

The calculation algorithms are independently implemented from the NEXRAD ICD
and SPC technical documentation. The parameter definitions (STP, SCP, SHIP,
SHERB, etc.) follow published formulas from Thompson et al., Sherburn et al.,
Craven & Brooks, and other peer-reviewed sources.

The rendering approach draws from techniques in the rustdar and wrf-rust-plots
projects by FahrenheitResearch.
